channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins project -- Jenkins Skytap Cloud CI Plugin

item.title: CVE-2019-10366|2024-08-04T22:17:20.576Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20skytap%20cloud%20ci%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Skytap Cloud CI Plugin 2.06 and earlier stored credentials unencrypted in job config.xml files on the Jenkins master where they could be viewed by users with Extended Read permission, or access to the master file system.

item.title: CVE-2020-2157|2024-08-04T07:01:41.117Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20skytap%20cloud%20ci%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Skytap Cloud CI Plugin 2.07 and earlier transmits configured credentials in plain text as part of job configuration forms, potentially resulting in their exposure.
